**Request:**
```bash
curl -X PUT http://localhost:3001/api/workflows/65a1234567890abcdef12346 \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "name": "Updated: Fetch and Store Orders",
    "description": "Improved workflow"
  }'
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "workflow": {
    "_id": "65a1234567890abcdef12346",
    "name": "Updated: Fetch and Store Orders",
    "description": "Improved workflow",
