## Error Examples

### Invalid Workflow ID
```json
{
  "error": "Workflow not found"
}
```

### Workflow Not Published
```json
{
  "error": "Workflow must be published to execute"
}
```

### Rate Limit Exceeded
```json
{
  "error": "Rate limit exceeded: 100 runs per hour"
}
```

### MongoDB Connection Error
```json
{
  "error": "MongoDB operation failed: connection refused"
}
```

