## Monitoring

### Check Temporal UI
```
http://localhost:8080
```

### Check Temporal Namespace
```bash
# List running workflows
temporal workflow list

# Get workflow details
temporal workflow show --workflow-id workflow-65a1234567890abcdef12346-1705311000000

# View workflow history
temporal workflow show --workflow-id workflow-65a1234567890abcdef12346-1705311000000 --output json
```

### Check MongoDB
```bash
# Connect to MongoDB
mongosh "mongodb+srv://workflow_user:password@cluster.mongodb.net/workflow-db"

# List workflows
db.workflows.find()

# List runs
db.workflow_runs.find().sort({ createdAt: -1 }).limit(10)
```
